                    "name": "Cairn Wight Spawn",
                    "type": "stat_block_section",
                    "text": "A living humanoid slain by a cairn wight's weapon or claw Strike rises as a spawned wight after 1d4 rounds. This spawned wight is under the command of the cairn wight that killed it. It doesn't have drain life or cairn wight spawn and is <a aonid=\"3\" game-obj=\"Conditions\">clumsy 2</a> for as long as it is a spawned wight. If its creator dies, the spawned wight becomes a full-fledged, autonomous cairn wight; it regains its free will, gains drain life and cairn wight spawn, and is no longer clumsy.",
